bug.short_desc: Bugzilla should support streaming for attachments

long_desc.thetext: The Bugzilla attachment handler does not support streaming but copies the attachment into memory. BugzillaTaskAttachmentHandler.getContent() should return a stream from the HTTP connection instead.
